pages.text: Ars Nouveau 1.9.0, Trees, Autocrafting, oh my! $(li)Adds the Wixie, an auto crafting friend!$(li)Adds four new Archwood Trees$(li)Adds the casting wand$(li)Fixed interact with items on the whelp. Cake farms are now possible!$(li)New decorative stone variants$(li)New block textures
